---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import { Container } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
---

<Layout>
  <Container>
    <div class="py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-12 text-center">Comprehensive Care</h1>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Home Medical Visits</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Dedicated doctors and nurses providing professional care, wound management, and health monitoring at your doorstep.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Ground Ambulance</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Our fleet is equipped with life-support systems for rapid and safe patient transfers across the island.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Medical Equipment Rental</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">From hospital beds to oxygen concentrators, we provide the tools you need for effective home-based recovery.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Air Escorts</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Qualified medical personnel to accompany patients on commercial or private flights for safe transit.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Palliative Care</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Focusing on quality of life, our team provides pain management and emotional support for long-term health journeys.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
